wlsxWlanMIB.name: wlsxWlanMIB
wlsxWlanMIB.contactinfo: Postal: 1322 Crossman Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: dl-support@arubanetworks.com Phone: +1 408 227 4500
wlsxWlanMIB.description: This MIB module defines MIB objects which provide information about the Wireless Management System (WMS) in the Aruba Controller.

wlsxWlanTotalNumAccessPoints.name: wlsxWlanTotalNumAccessPoints
wlsxWlanTotalNumAccessPoints.description: Total Number of Access Points connected to the controller.

wlsxWlanTotalNumStationsAssociated.name: wlsxWlanTotalNumStationsAssociated
wlsxWlanTotalNumStationsAssociated.description: Total Number of Stations Associated to the controller.

wlsxWlanAPGroupTable.name: wlsxWlanAPGroupTable
wlsxWlanAPGroupTable.description: This Table lists all the Access Points Groups configured in the Aruba controller.

wlanAPGroup.name: wlanAPGroup
wlanAPGroup.description: The name of an AP group

wlanAPNumAps.name: wlanAPNumAps
wlanAPNumAps.description: The number of APs in the AP Group

wlsxWlanAPTable.name: wlsxWlanAPTable
wlsxWlanAPTable.description: This table lists all the Access Points connected to the controller.

wlanAPMacAddress.name: wlanAPMacAddress
wlanAPMacAddress.description: Ethernet MAC Address of the Access Point

wlanAPIpAddress.name: wlanAPIpAddress
wlanAPIpAddress.description: IP Address of the Access Point

wlanAPName.name: wlanAPName
wlanAPName.description: Host name of the Access Point.

wlanAPGroupName.name: wlanAPGroupName
wlanAPGroupName.description: Group Name of the Access Point.

wlanAPModel.name: wlanAPModel
wlanAPModel.description: Sys OID of the Access Point.

wlanAPSerialNumber.name: wlanAPSerialNumber
wlanAPSerialNumber.description: Serial Number of the Access Point.

wlanAPNumRadios.name: wlanAPNumRadios
wlanAPNumRadios.description: Number of Radios in the Access Point.

wlanAPEnet1Mode.name: wlanAPEnet1Mode
wlanAPEnet1Mode.description: Enet1 Mode of the Access Point.

wlanAPIpsecMode.name: wlanAPIpsecMode
wlanAPIpsecMode.description: IPSEC Mode of the Access Point.

wlanAPUpTime.name: wlanAPUpTime
wlanAPUpTime.description: Time (in hundredths of seconds) since the last time the Access Point bootstrapped with the controller.

wlanAPModelName.name: wlanAPModelName
wlanAPModelName.description: Model name of the Access Point.

wlanAPNumBootstraps.name: wlanAPNumBootstraps
wlanAPNumBootstraps.description: Number of times the AP has bootstrapped with the controller.

wlanAPNumReboots.name: wlanAPNumReboots
wlanAPNumReboots.description: Number of times the AP has rebooted.

wlanAPUnprovisioned.name: wlanAPUnprovisioned
wlanAPUnprovisioned.description: Indicates whether the AP is unprovisioned due to lack of antenna gain or location code settings.

wlanAPMonitorMode.name: wlanAPMonitorMode
wlanAPMonitorMode.description: Indicates whether any radio on this AP is acting as an air monitor.

wlanAPFQLNBuilding.name: wlanAPFQLNBuilding
wlanAPFQLNBuilding.description: The building component of the AP's FQLN.

wlanAPFQLNFloor.name: wlanAPFQLNFloor
wlanAPFQLNFloor.description: The floor component of the AP's FQLN.

wlanAPFQLN.name: wlanAPFQLN
wlanAPFQLN.description: The AP's Fully Qualified Location Name (FQLN).

wlanAPFQLNCampus.name: wlanAPFQLNCampus
wlanAPFQLNCampus.description: The campus component of the AP's FQLN.

wlanAPLongitude.name: wlanAPLongitude
wlanAPLongitude.description: Longitude of the AP. Signed floating-point value.

wlanAPLatitude.name: wlanAPLatitude
wlanAPLatitude.description: Latitude of the AP. Signed floating-point value.

wlanAPAltitude.name: wlanAPAltitude
wlanAPAltitude.description: Altitude of the AP. Signed floating-point value.

wlsxWlanRadioTable.name: wlsxWlanRadioTable
wlsxWlanRadioTable.description: This table lists all the radios known to the controller.

wlanAPRadioChannel.name: wlanAPRadioChannel
wlanAPRadioChannel.description: The channel the radio is currently operating on.

wlanAPRadioTransmitPower.name: wlanAPRadioTransmitPower
wlanAPRadioTransmitPower.description: The current power level of the radio.

wlanAPRadioMode.name: wlanAPRadioMode
wlanAPRadioMode.description: The Mode in which the radio is operating.

wlanAPRadioUtilization.name: wlanAPRadioUtilization
wlanAPRadioUtilization.description: The Utilization of the radio as a percentage of the total capacity.

wlanAPRadioNumAssociatedClients.name: wlanAPRadioNumAssociatedClients
wlanAPRadioNumAssociatedClients.description: The number of Clients associated to this radio.

wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredClients.name: wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredClients
wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredClients.description: The number of Clients this Radio is monitoring.

wlanAPRadioNumActiveBSSIDs.name: wlanAPRadioNumActiveBSSIDs
wlanAPRadioNumActiveBSSIDs.description: The number of active BSSIDs on this Radio.

wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredBSSIDs.name: wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredBSSIDs
wlanAPRadioNumMonitoredBSSIDs.description: The number of AP BSSIDs this radio is monitoring.

wlanAPRadioBearing.name: wlanAPRadioBearing
wlanAPRadioBearing.description: Antenna Bearing in degrees from True North. Unsigned floating-point value. Range: 0-360.

wlanAPRadioTiltAngle.name: wlanAPRadioTiltAngle
wlanAPRadioTiltAngle.description: Tilt angle of antenna in degrees. -ve for downtilt, +ve for uptilt. Signed floating-point value. Range: -90 to +90.

wlanAPRadioHTMode.name: wlanAPRadioHTMode
wlanAPRadioHTMode.description: The HT mode of the radio, if any.

wlanAPRadioHTExtChannel.name: wlanAPRadioHTExtChannel
wlanAPRadioHTExtChannel.description: Indicates the offset of the 40MHz extension channel, if any.

wlanAPRadioHTChannel.name: wlanAPRadioHTChannel
wlanAPRadioHTChannel.description: A display string indicating the current channel. If wlanAPRadioHTExtChannel is set to 'above' or 'below', then the channel number will be appended with '+' or '-' respectively.

wlanAPRadioAPName.name: wlanAPRadioAPName
wlanAPRadioAPName.description: Name of the AP the radio belongs to

wlsxWlanAPBssidTable.name: wlsxWlanAPBssidTable
wlsxWlanAPBssidTable.description: This table lists all the BSSIDs active on this controller.

wlanAPBSSID.name: wlanAPBSSID
wlanAPBSSID.description: The MAC address of the Access Point.

wlanAPBssidSlot.name: wlanAPBssidSlot
wlanAPBssidSlot.description: Slot to which the Access Point is connected.

wlanAPBssidPort.name: wlanAPBssidPort
wlanAPBssidPort.description: Port to which the Access Point is connected.

wlanAPBssidPhyType.name: wlanAPBssidPhyType
wlanAPBssidPhyType.description: Physical Layer Protocol support of the AP.

wlanAPBssidMode.name: wlanAPBssidMode
wlanAPBssidMode.description: Indicates whether the Access point is an Air Monitor or regular AP or Mesh Portal or Mesh Point.

wlanAPBssidUpTime.name: wlanAPBssidUpTime
wlanAPBssidUpTime.description: Time (in hundredths of seconds) since the tunnel was created between the access point and controller

wlanAPBssidInactiveTime.name: wlanAPBssidInactiveTime
wlanAPBssidInactiveTime.description: Time (in hundredths of seconds) since any activity took place on the BSSID.

wlanAPBssidLoadBalancing.name: wlanAPBssidLoadBalancing
wlanAPBssidLoadBalancing.description: Indicates whether load balancing is enabled or not.

wlanAPBssidNumAssociatedStations.name: wlanAPBssidNumAssociatedStations
wlanAPBssidNumAssociatedStations.description: Indicates the number of stations associated to this BSSID.

wlanAPBssidAPMacAddress.name: wlanAPBssidAPMacAddress
wlanAPBssidAPMacAddress.description: Indicates the Access Point to which this BSSID belongs.

wlanAPBssidPhyNumber.name: wlanAPBssidPhyNumber
wlanAPBssidPhyNumber.description: Indicates the radio number to which this BSSID belongs.

wlanAPBssidHTMode.name: wlanAPBssidHTMode
wlanAPBssidHTMode.description: Indicates the HT mode of this BSSID, if any.

wlanAPBssidHTExtChannel.name: wlanAPBssidHTExtChannel
wlanAPBssidHTExtChannel.description: Indicates the offset of the 40MHz extension channel, if any.

wlanAPBssidHTChannel.name: wlanAPBssidHTChannel
wlanAPBssidHTChannel.description: A display string indicating the current channel. If wlanAPBssidHTExtChannel is set to 'above' or 'below', then the channel number will be appended with '+' or '-' respectively.

wlanAPBssidModule.name: wlanAPBssidModule
wlanAPBssidModule.description: Module to which the Access Point is connected.

wlsxWlanESSIDTable.name: wlsxWlanESSIDTable
wlsxWlanESSIDTable.description: This Table lists all the ESSIDs advertised by this controller.

wlanESSIDNumStations.name: wlanESSIDNumStations
wlanESSIDNumStations.description: The number of stations connected to this ESSID.

wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsUp.name: wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsUp
wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsUp.description: The number of APs currently advertising this ESSID.

wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsDown.name: wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsDown
wlanESSIDNumAccessPointsDown.description: The number of APs configured to advertise this ESSID that are not currently operational.

wlanESSIDEncryptionType.name: wlanESSIDEncryptionType
wlanESSIDEncryptionType.description: The encryption methods supported on this ESSID.

wlsxWlanESSIDVlanPoolTable.name: wlsxWlanESSIDVlanPoolTable
wlsxWlanESSIDVlanPoolTable.description: This Table lists all the VLANs associated with this ESSID.

wlanESSIDVlanId.name: wlanESSIDVlanId
wlanESSIDVlanId.description: VLAN which is part of the VLAN pool for this ESSID.

wlanESSIDVlanPoolStatus.name: wlanESSIDVlanPoolStatus
wlanESSIDVlanPoolStatus.description: Row status object used to indicate the status of the row.

wlsxWlanStationTable.name: wlsxWlanStationTable
wlsxWlanStationTable.description: This Table lists all the wireless stations associated with the Access points connected to this controller.

wlanStaPhyAddress.name: wlanStaPhyAddress
wlanStaPhyAddress.description: The Physical Address of the Station.

wlanStaApBssid.name: wlanStaApBssid
wlanStaApBssid.description: The Access point to which this station last associated to.

wlanStaIsAuthenticated.name: wlanStaIsAuthenticated
wlanStaIsAuthenticated.description: Indicates whether the station is authenticated.

wlanStaIsAssociated.name: wlanStaIsAssociated
wlanStaIsAssociated.description: Indicates whether the station is associated.

wlanStaChannel.name: wlanStaChannel
wlanStaChannel.description: Channel on which the station is associated.

wlanStaVlanId.name: wlanStaVlanId
wlanStaVlanId.description: VLAN in which the station is present.

wlanStaVOIPState.name: wlanStaVOIPState
wlanStaVOIPState.description: The State of VoIP for this station.

wlanStaVOIPProtocol.name: wlanStaVOIPProtocol
wlanStaVOIPProtocol.description: If VoIP is enabled, the type of the protocol supported.

wlanStaTransmitRate.name: wlanStaTransmitRate
wlanStaTransmitRate.description: Transmit rate with which the Station is associated with this system.

wlanStaAssociationID.name: wlanStaAssociationID
wlanStaAssociationID.description: AID with which the Station is associated with this system.

wlanStaPhyNumber.name: wlanStaPhyNumber
wlanStaPhyNumber.description: Radio PHY number to which the station is associated

wlanStaRSSI.name: wlanStaRSSI
wlanStaRSSI.description: Signal to Noise ratio for the station.

wlanStaUpTime.name: wlanStaUpTime
wlanStaUpTime.description: Time since the station associated to the current BSSID.

wlanStaHTMode.name: wlanStaHTMode
wlanStaHTMode.description: The HT status of the station.

wlsxWlanStaAssociationFailureTable.name: wlsxWlanStaAssociationFailureTable
wlsxWlanStaAssociationFailureTable.description: This Table lists all the stations and the BSSID's to which they failed to associate. Once a station successfully associates, association failure entries are not reported for that station.

wlanStaAssocFailureApName.name: wlanStaAssocFailureApName
wlanStaAssocFailureApName.description: Name of the Access Point to which this station tried to associate.

wlanStaAssocFailureApEssid.name: wlanStaAssocFailureApEssid
wlanStaAssocFailureApEssid.description: ESSID to which the station association failed.

wlanStaAssocFailurePhyNum.name: wlanStaAssocFailurePhyNum
wlanStaAssocFailurePhyNum.description: Radio PHY number to which the station tried to associate.

wlanStaAssocFailurePhyType.name: wlanStaAssocFailurePhyType
wlanStaAssocFailurePhyType.description: Radio PHY Type of the Station.

wlanStaAssocFailureElapsedTime.name: wlanStaAssocFailureElapsedTime
wlanStaAssocFailureElapsedTime.description: Elapsed time in timeticks after the station's failure to associate.

wlanStaAssocFailureReason.name: wlanStaAssocFailureReason
wlanStaAssocFailureReason.description: Reason for the Station association failure

wlanAPChTransmittedFragmentCount.name: wlanAPChTransmittedFragmentCount
wlanAPChTransmittedFragmentCount.description: This counter shall be incremented for an acknowledged MPDU with an individual address in the address 1 field or an MPDU with a multicast address in the address 1 field of type Data or Management.

wlanAPChMulticastTransmittedFrameCount.name: wlanAPChMulticastTransmittedFrameCount
wlanAPChMulticastTransmittedFrameCount.description: This counter shall increment only when the multicast bit is set in the destination MAC address of a successfully transmitted MSDU. When operating as a STA in an ESS, where these frames are directed to the AP, this implies having received an acknowledgment to all associated MPDUs.

wlanAPChFailedCount.name: wlanAPChFailedCount
wlanAPChFailedCount.description: This counter shall increment when an MSDU is not transmitted successfully due to the number of transmit attempts exceeding either the dot11ShortRetryLimit or dot11LongRetryLimit.

wlanAPChRetryCount.name: wlanAPChRetryCount
wlanAPChRetryCount.description: This counter shall increment when an MSDU is successfully transmitted after one or more retransmissions.

wlanAPChMultipleRetryCount.name: wlanAPChMultipleRetryCount
wlanAPChMultipleRetryCount.description: This counter shall increment when an MSDU is successfully transmitted after more than one retransmission.

wlanAPChFrameDuplicateCount.name: wlanAPChFrameDuplicateCount
wlanAPChFrameDuplicateCount.description: This counter shall increment when a frame is received that the Sequence Control field indicates is a duplicate.

wlanAPChRTSSuccessCount.name: wlanAPChRTSSuccessCount
wlanAPChRTSSuccessCount.description: This counter shall increment when a CTS is received in response to an RTS.

wlanAPChRTSFailureCount.name: wlanAPChRTSFailureCount
wlanAPChRTSFailureCount.description: This counter shall increment when a CTS is not received in response to an RTS.

wlanAPChACKFailureCount.name: wlanAPChACKFailureCount
wlanAPChACKFailureCount.description: This counter shall increment when an ACK is not received when expected.

wlanAPChReceivedFragmentCount.name: wlanAPChReceivedFragmentCount
wlanAPChReceivedFragmentCount.description: This counter shall be incremented for each successfully received MPDU of type Data or Management.

wlanAPChMulticastReceivedFrameCount.name: wlanAPChMulticastReceivedFrameCount
wlanAPChMulticastReceivedFrameCount.description: This counter shall increment when a MSDU is received with the multicast bit set in the destination MAC address.

wlanAPChFCSErrorCount.name: wlanAPChFCSErrorCount
wlanAPChFCSErrorCount.description: This counter shall increment when an FCS error is detected in a received MPDU.

wlanAPChTransmittedFrameCount.name: wlanAPChTransmittedFrameCount
wlanAPChTransmittedFrameCount.description: This counter shall increment for each successfully transmitted MSDU.

wlanAPChWEPUndecryptableCount.name: wlanAPChWEPUndecryptableCount
wlanAPChWEPUndecryptableCount.description: This counter shall increment when a frame is received with the Protected Frame subfield of the Frame Control field set to one and the WEPOn value for the key mapped to the transmitter's MAC address indicates that the frame should not have been encrypted or that frame is discarded due to the receiving STA not implementing the privacy option.
